parameters:
\FF[tubaki_trouble]Tsubaki: "Suzaku-san! Ugh... It's my fault for not guiding
you properly, and now you've become a delinquent..."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[tubaki_trouble]\AA[2]Tsubaki: "But to not even greet someone in the hallway...
And you're the president of the Detective Club..."
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[tubaki_trouble]\AA[2]Tsubaki: "A reason to become a delinquent? Could it be..."

\FF[tubaki_reverse]Tsubaki: "Something like this~? Kyahaha! The pounding feels
so good~♪ Doing it in the school hallway is just the best❤"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[tubaki_reverse]\AA[2]Tsubaki: "Don't get cocky with me! Talking like I'm some
kind of fool!! Aaahn? I'll teach you a lesson!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[tubaki_reverse]\AA[2]Tsubaki: "I'll turn you into a bitchy gal so embarrassing
you can't be taken anywhere!! Kihhihih...!!"

gal♪ No need for lessons~!"

\F[beni_reverse1]\FF[tubaki_reverse]\AA[2]Tsubaki: "You bet I will♪ I'll mess you up to the point of
ruining your life! Kyahahah...!!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[tubaki_reverse]\AA[2]Tsubaki: "Everyone♥ I'm going to turn you into shameless
bitchy gals that you can't take anywhere!!"
